SUMMARY:GTApreneurs April 15-2026 Afternoon Virtual Business Networking Ev
 ent Toronto
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Women in Business Networking Group (TWIB)\n\\*\\*You n
 eed to register on our website to attend this event and get the zoom link.
  RSVPing on Meetup does not mean that you are registered\, even though Mee
 tup.com will send you an email saying that you have. Thank you. Please go 
 here: https://gtapreneurs.com/networking-events-toronto\n\n\\*Please note 
 this event is advertised on multiple platforms\, and we expect around 20-2
 5 guests.\n\nDo you want more clients? Join us for GTApreneurs April 15-20
 26 Afternoon Virtual Business Networking Event to connect with other amazi
 ng entrepreneurs\, learn something new and promote your business!\n\n**WAR
 M-UP ITINERARY:**\n\n* **[11:45am-12pm: Pre-event networking]**\n* **12:00
 -12:10pm:** GTApreneurs welcoming presentation\n* **12:10-12:30pm:** Featu
 red Presentation: Tammy Defore\, ***“How Big is Your Sales Funnel?”***
 \n* **12:30-1:00pm:** Elevator Pitches (45 seconds each)\nFree\n\n**PREMIU
 M EVENT ITINERARY:**\n\n* **[11:45am-12pm: Pre-event networking]**\n* **12
 :00-12:10pm:** GTApreneurs welcoming presentation\n* **12:10-12:30pm:** Fe
 atured Presentation: Tammy Defore\, ***“How Big is Your Sales Funnel?”
 ***\n* **12:30-1:00pm:** Elevator Pitches (45 seconds each)\n* **1:00-2:00
 pm:** Breakout rooms (Network 1-1 with other guests)\n\n**TICKETS**\n**GTA
 preneurs' Referral Group\, Exhibitor and Mega Networking Members:** Free\n
 **Non-members:** $10\n\\*Premium ticket includes Guest Contact sheet email
 ed to you after the event. Note: You must attend the event to receive the 
 guest contact sheet.\n\nThis event will feature our President of GTApreneu
 rs\, **Tammy Defoe**\, who excels at helping entrepreneurs get more exposu
 re and more clients. She is a Business Coach and Consultant specializing i
 n business development\, sales\, marketing\, digital marketing\, public sp
 eaking\, business communication and networking. If you would like 1-1 assi
 stance for your business\, visit https://gtapreneurs.com/business-coaching
 -toronto to learn more about her services and book a free video call at ht
 tps://gtapreneurs.zohobookings.ca/#/gtapreneursinc2 to talk about what you
  need to get your business moving in the right direction.\n\n**QUESTIONS?*
 * Contact GTApreneurs at 416-522-7770 or info@gtapreneurs.com\n\nWant to a
 ttend the Premium version of our Virtual Networking Events for FREE? Becom
 e a Member. Learn more at https://gtapreneurs.com/business-networking-memb
 erships\n\nWe look forward to seeing you at the event!\n\nGTApreneurs Team
