SUMMARY:GTApreneurs May 6-2026 Downtown Toronto Business Networking Event
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Women in Business Networking Group (TWIB)\nJoin us for
  a vibrant Business Networking Event in Toronto where you may meet your ne
 xt client\, referral partner or friend. Discover opportunities and connect
 ! Register now.\n\n**REGISTER HERE:** https://gtapreneurs.com/networking-e
 vents-toronto\n\n**VENUE:** Office Evolution\n**ADDRESS:** 197 Yonge St\, 
 Suites 201 & 202 Toronto\, ON (Across from CF Eaton Centre)\n**TRANSIT:** 
 Get off at Queen subway station\, walk through the mall\, up to the 2nd fl
 oor and out the front door.\n**PARKING:** Under Eaton Centre (payment requ
 ired)\n\n**ITINERARY:**\n\n* **6:00-6:55pm:** Open networking\n* **6:55-7:
 05pm:** Host & Sponsor presentations\n* **7:05-8:00pm:** Open networking\n
 \n\\*Appetizers and beverages provided.\n\n**TICKETS:**\n**GTApreneurs' Re
 ferral Group\, Exhibitor and Mega Networking Members:** Free\n**Non-member
 s:** $20\n***\\*Includes a Guest Contact Sheet*** emailed to you the day a
 fter the event. Note: You need to attend the event to receive the sheet.\n
 \n**HOSTS:**\n**Tammy Defoe\,** President of GTApreneurs\nLearn more about
  Tammy’s Coaching services at www.gtapreneurs.com/business-coaching-toro
 nto\n\n**QUESTIONS ABOUT THE EVENT?** Call 416-522-7770 or email info@gtap
 reneurs.com\n\nand\n\n**Mohammad Reza Sadeghian\,** Managing Director at O
 ffice Evolution.\n\nMohammad is the Manager at Office Evolution Downtown T
 oronto\, where he leads the growth of a flexible and professional workspac
 e for entrepreneurs and businesses. He is dedicated to building a collabor
 ative community and supporting clients in achieving their business goals.\
 n\n**CONTACT MOHAMMAD:** [www.officeevolution.com/locations/canada/ontario
 /toronto](www.officeevolution.com/locations/canada/ontario/toronto) \\| 41
 6\\-540\\-0856 \\| mohammad\\.sadeghian@officeevolution\\.com\n\nView all 
 of GTApreneurs events and services at www.gtapreneurs.com\n\nWe look forwa
 rd to seeing you there!
