SUMMARY:GTApreneurs BizX 2026 Business Expo and Conference – VIP Ticket
DESCRIPTION:Toronto Women in Business Networking Group (TWIB)\nYou are inv
 ited to an exciting mega networking bash! Join us on **Tuesday\, October 2
 0\, 2026** for **GTApreneurs’** **BizX 2026 Business Expo and Conference
 !** We expect 300+ small business owners and entrepreneurs all looking to 
 meet you and many others to do business together!\n\n**REGISTER HERE** \\>
 \\> [https://gtapreneurs.com/bizx-2026-business-expo](https://gtapreneurs.
 com/bizx-2026-business-expo)\n\n**DOOR PRIZE RAFFLE:** Bring your business
  card and drop it in the box for a chance to win a great prize.\n\n**BIZX 
 2026 BUSINESS EXPO CONTEST:** Each time you visit an exhibitor\, and excha
 nge business cards (or exchange information electronically)\, they will pu
 t a sticker on your event map. Fill your map with a sticker from every exh
 ibitor to win a prize. At the end of the day (4:30-5:00pm)\, we will annou
 nce Expo Contest winners as well as guest door prize winners and exhibitor
  draw winners.\n\n**VIP TICKET ITINERARY:**\n\n* **9:00-10:30am:** Registr
 ation + Continental breakfast + Networking\n* **10:30-10:45am:** GTApreneu
 rs welcoming presentation\n* **10:45-11:00am:** Platinum and Gold Sponsor 
 Introductions\n* **11:00-11:20am:** Featured Speaker 1 presentation\n* **1
 1:20-11:40am:** Featured Speaker 2 presentation\n* **11:40-12:00pm:** Feat
 ured Speaker 3 presentation\n* **12:15-2:00pm: VIP Lunch** (Vegetarian\, v
 egan and gluten-free options available)\n* **12:30-4:15pm:** BizX 2026 Exp
 o\n* **2:30-3:00pm:** Featured Speaker 4 presentation\n* **4:30-5:00pm:** 
 ***Awards ceremony*** >*BizX 2026 Expo Contest winners\, guest door prize 
 draw\, exhibitor draw > **Great prizes to be won!***\n\n\\*Refreshments av
 ailable all day – Coffee\, tea\, juice\, pop\, water\n\\*Snacks availabl
 e until 4:15pm\n\n**VIP TICKETS:**\n\n* $59 regular or $49 until August 31
 \, 2026\n* Free for Mega\, Exhibitor and Referral Group members\n\n**Not a
  member?** Join us today >> https://gtapreneurs.com/business-networking-me
 mberships\n\n**Book an exhibitor table at BizX 2026\,** click here >> [htt
 ps://gtapreneurs.com/product/bizx2026-business-expo-exhibitor](https://gta
 preneurs.com/product/bizx2026-business-expo-exhibitor)\n\n**Sponsor BizX 2
 026**\, send us a message >> info@gtapreneurs.com\n\n**SPONSORED BY:**\n\n
 * **Gorette Marques\,** Global Bricks Realty\, www.gmarquesrealtor.com\n* 
 **Sonia Kurmey\,** Arbonne\, www.soniakurmey.arbonne.com\n* **Balbir Pabil
 a\,** PPLSI\\~LegalShield\, https://bkpabila.ladiesofjustice.ca\n\n**DISCL
 AIMERS**\n\n***Event Photo and Video Disclaimer:*** By registering for and
 /or attending GTApreneurs (“Us” and “Our” and “We”) Events\, y
 ou give Us consent to use your image and/or video for Our publications\, a
 dvertising and/or other media activities (including the Internet).\n\n***I
 nformation Sharing:*** By registering for or attending a GTApreneurs netwo
 rking event\, you are agreeing to share your name\, professional title\, o
 rganization name\, city\, website (if given) and LinkedIn URL (if given) w
 ith the other event attendees who attend that event. If you indicate in yo
 ur registration form that you give Us permission to share your phone numbe
 r and/or your email address with the other event attendees\, we will share
  the information you give Us permission to share. If you indicate in the r
 egistration form that you don’t give Us permission to share your phone n
 umber and/or your email address with the other attendees\, We will not sha
 re it with the other attendees. GTApreneurs will never share your home add
 ress with anyone.\n\n***Event Guest Contact Sheet:*** If you don’t atten
 d an event\, you will not be given the guest contact sheet and your name o
 r other information will not appear on the sheet.
